HEADWORD: Doxology
<hw>Dox*ol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Doxologies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[LL.
